Package: CDREGM
Title: Capitalism, Democracy and Rule of Law Economic Growth Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Cesar", "Garcia", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "gypsaman@gmail.com"),
    person("Felipe", "Llaugel", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Implements economic growth models within the Capitalism,
    Democracy, and Rule of Law (CDR) framework. Provides tools for
    estimating, comparing, and visualising the joint effects of
    institutional quality, democratic governance, and property-rights
    protection on long-run economic growth. Supports panel-data
    estimation, robustness diagnostics, and replication workflows
    common in comparative political economy research.
